'''拉合尔皇家浴室'''（Shahi Hammam；[[乌尔都语|乌尔都语]]、{{lang-pa|{{Nastaliq|شاہی حمام}}}}）又名'''瓦齐尔汗浴室''', 是[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[拉合尔|拉合尔]]的一个波斯风格的[[土耳其浴|土耳其浴室]]，建于1635年，皇帝[[沙贾汉|沙贾汉]]统治期间。修建者是莫卧儿宫廷的首席医生伊拉姆-乌丁安萨里，人称瓦齐尔汗。<ref name="WKM">Asher, p.225</ref><ref>Shelomo Dov Goitein. [https://books.google.nl/books?id=cmn8U8uNtFAC&pg=PA170&dq=wazir+arabic+word&hl=nl&sa=X&ved=0CCAQ6AEwAGoVChMI28upua-LxgIVZivbCh0RbQDU#v=onepage&q=wazir%20arabic%20word&f=false ''Studies in Islamic History and Institutions''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.nl/books?id=cmn8U8uNtFAC&pg=PA170&dq=wazir+arabic+word&hl=nl&sa=X&ved=0CCAQ6AEwAGoVChMI28upua-LxgIVZivbCh0RbQDU#v=onepage&q=wazir%20arabic%20word&f=false |date=20201117102813 }} BRILL, 2010 {{ISBN|9004179313}} p 170</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Masjid Vazir K̲h̲ān|url=http://archnet.org/sites/1750|website=Archnet|accessdate=25 August 2016|quote=The mosque was founded by Hakim Ilmud Din Ansari, a distinguished physician from Chiniot who received the Ministerial title of 'Wazir Khan' under the reign of Shah Jahan, and was later promoted to the position of Viceroy of Punjab.|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225194546/http://archnet.org/sites/1750|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这个浴室是一个[[瓦合甫|瓦合甫]]，用于供养[[瓦齐尔汗清真寺|瓦齐尔汗清真寺]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=History and Background in Conservation of the Wazir Khan Mosque Lahore: Preliminary Report on Condition and Risk Assessment.|url=http://archnet.org/publications/6586|website=Aga Khan Historic Cities Programme|publisher=Aga Khan Cultural Services - Pakistan|accessdate=25 August 2016|date=2012|quote=The spectacular monumental ensemble of the Wazir Khan Mosque in the Walled City of Lahore was built in 1634 during the reign of the Mughal emperor Shah Jahan. Its endowment then comprised the congregational mosque, an elaborate forecourt, a serai, a hammam, a bazaar, and a special bazaar for calligraphers and bookbinders.|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225194548/http://archnet.org/publications/6586|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

浴室已不再使用，于2013年至2015年修复，大部分资金由[[挪威|挪威]]政府提供。2016年，浴室的成功保护修复工程获[[教科文组织|教科文组织]]授予的荣誉奖<ref>{{cite news|title=Lahore's Mughal-era Shahi Hammam wins UNESCO award|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/1175801/lahores-mughal-era-shahi-hammam-wins-unesco-award/|accessdate=22 December 2016|agency=Express Tribune|date=2016-09-04|archive-date=2018-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213063734/https://tribune.com.pk/story/1175801/lahores-mughal-era-shahi-hammam-wins-unesco-award/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

拉合尔皇家浴室位于[[拉合尔城墙|拉合尔城墙]]以内，距离[[德里门_(拉合尔)|德里门]]（Delhi Gate）只有几步之遥。拉合尔皇家浴室是[[拉合尔|拉合尔]]仅存的莫卧儿时代的土耳其浴室。<ref>{{cite web|title=Shahi Hammam Bathhouse|url=http://www.orientalarchitecture.com/sid/836/pakistan/lahore/shahi-hammam-bathhouse|website=Asian Historical Architecture|accessdate=27 August 2016|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225194551/https://www.orientalarchitecture.com/sid/836/pakistan/lahore/shahi-hammam-bathhouse|dead-url=no}}</ref>

